<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Story from Another Side of Heaven</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1ba5c8 0%, #0d8fa3 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .post-title {
            color: #1ba5c8;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .post-intro {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1ba5c8 0%, #0d8fa3 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .mission-section {
            background-color: #f9f7f4;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .mission-section h3 {
            color: #1ba5c8;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .mission-section p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #8b7355;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffc684;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .unsubscribe {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .unsubscribe a {
            color: #ffc684;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Another Side of Heaven</h1>
        <p>Serving God in the Caribbean</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="post-title">New Story from Our Mission</h2>

        <p class="post-intro">
            We've just shared a new chapter in our mission journey. Discover inspiring stories of faith, service, and the lives being touched through our work in the Virgin Islands.
        </p>

        <p><strong>{{ entry.title }}</strong></p>

        <a href="{{ entry.getUrl() }}?utm_source=email&utm_medium=newsletter&utm_campaign=blog_post&utm_content={{ entry.title|url_encode }}" class="cta-button">Read This Story →</a>

        <!-- Mission Info -->
        <div class="mission-section">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>Serving the people of St. Thomas and St. John in our Savior's way, sharing the gospel through faith, service, and community.</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider">

        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
            Join us as we continue this beautiful work.
            <a href="{{ siteUrl('contact') }}" style="color: #1ba5c8; text-decoration: none;">Get in touch</a> to learn how you can be part of this journey.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>Another Side of Heaven</strong></p>
        <p>Serving God's people in the Caribbean</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
            <a href="{{ siteUrl() }}">Home</a> •
            <a href="{{ siteUrl('blog') }}">Blog</a> •
            <a href="{{ siteUrl('contact') }}">Contact</a>
        </p>
        {% set footer = craft.app.globals().getSetByHandle('footer') %}
        <div class="unsubscribe">
            <p><a href="{{ siteUrl('actions/site/form/unsubscribe?id=' ~ subscriberId) }}">Unsubscribe from these emails</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.8;">©{{ "now"|date('Y') }} {{ siteName }}. {{ footer.copyright }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>